{"tid":1387434,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好心痛咁多前線被捉！！！緊要關頭就個個向後散！！！","createTime":"2019-07-30T14:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T14:26:57.000Z","uid":217242,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c2f40dc90df666c9be0e87eaab0cf0c9fb25a9e9","tid":1387434,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:00:34.000Z","msg":"雖然每位前線口中都講話預咗俾人捉，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但又有邊個係想爭取自由變咗失去自由！</span></span></span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n28號夜晚發夢見住班手足俾人捉<br />\n係個刻我猶豫應該向前幫手定走 <br />\n因為得我同幾個人衝係無補於事<br />\n<br />\n當時我無特別向後散 只係後退幾步<br />\n可能你會有疑問 因為我企係中間 <br />\n唔係最勇武個批 但其實我好想衝！<br />\n<br />\n我真係好希望有一個leader可以帶領我地一齊人海戰術反攻班狗，但事實係人地一衝我地就一盤散沙咁<br />\n個情況就好似未打就認輸 自亂陣腳<br />\n<br />\n各位兄弟姊妹！我真係唔想再見到有人被捉，我好後悔我無出手救佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好想下次再有機會係全部兄弟唔會猶豫一齊衝去救返手足返黎 因為我相信有好多人都係等緊人帶領而唔敢一個人衝<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/58NtO8X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F58NtO8X.png&h=b11e3b56&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99570ee35c684c13ac66824421a0a9ddafd5348a","tid":1387434,"uid":217242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:03:09.000Z","msg":"團結一致 不畏速龍！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0631776f507aced8304250a9c8c7b9253ce7e8a7","tid":1387434,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:05:31.000Z","msg":"點解速龍小隊一出 我地就要縮！！<br />\n我想拉返d手足返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2a42ac4a568ca6392d84bf45ff69849c227fc5","tid":1387434,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:10:56.000Z","msg":"我想下次同咁多位一齊救人返黎！<br />\n企得係前線都最少坐兩年 <br />\n大家要爭取下次唔好俾手足咁蝕章！<br />\n心態決定一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b89562bb4071be77aaa50dbae5590dc67adf2a7","tid":1387434,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:12:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">心態決定一切呀！！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319726ac0a64bddf2f7b4